🧠 Smart Task Planner

A smart productivity tool built to help users efficiently plan, organize, and track their daily tasks.
This project provides an intuitive interface to add, manage, and visualize tasks, along with smart prioritization and reminders.

🚀 Features

📅 Create, edit, and delete tasks easily
⏰ Set deadlines and reminders
⭐ Prioritize tasks by urgency or importance
📊 View daily / weekly summary of completed tasks
☁️ Persistent storage (local or cloud-ready)
🧠 Smart recommendations for time optimization (optional ML logic can be integrated)

🏗️ Tech Stack

Frontend: HTML, CSS, JavaScript (or React, if applicable)
Backend: Java / Spring Boot (customize as per your project)
Database: MySQL / SQLite / Firebase
Version Control: Git & GitHub

⚙️ Installation

Clone the repository:
git clone https://github.com/Vishall1221/Smart_Task_Planner.git

Navigate to the project folder:
cd Smart_Task_Planner

If you’re using Maven:
mvn clean install


Run the application:
java -jar target/Smart_Task_Planner.jar

🧩 Folder Structure
Smart_Task_Planner/
├── src/
│   ├── main/
│   │   ├── java/
│   │   └── resources/
│   └── test/
